unite-sorce for BEAR (inspired by unite-rails)

bear-project:
  http://code.google.com/p/bear-project/

Usage:
  Unite bear/App
    : BEAR_HOME/App/
      (igore directory: App/Form/, App/Page/, App/Ro/)

  Unite bear/htdocs
    : BEAR_HOME/htdocs/
      (igore directory: htdocs/__bear/, htdocs/__edit/, htdocs/__panda/)

  Unite bear/libs
    : BEAR_HOME/libs/

  Unite bear/Form
    : BEAR_HOME/App/Form/

  Unite bear/Page
    : BEAR_HOME/App/Page/

  Unite bear/Ro
    : BEAR_HOME/App/Ro/

  Unite bear/views
    : BEAR_HOME/App/views/


Key Map example.

nnoremap <silent> bh :<C-u>UniteWithInput bear/htdocs<CR>
nnoremap <silent> ba :<C-u>UniteWithInput bear/App<CR>
nnoremap <silent> bf :<C-u>UniteWithInput bear/Form<CR>
nnoremap <silent> bp :<C-u>UniteWithInput bear/Page<CR>
nnoremap <silent> br :<C-u>UniteWithInput bear/Ro<CR>
nnoremap <silent> bl :<C-u>UniteWithInput bear/libs<CR>
nnoremap <silent> bv :<C-u>UniteWithInput bear/views<CR>
